Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Pope visits Poland
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b040by86
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 10 Jun 1979
Pope John Paul II returns to his Polish homeland. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.